<title>KAN PATHIAN NIH KHUAL TLAWNG MI KHA CH351</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan Pathian nih khual tlawngmi kha, Biakar fekbik kha a pek, Vawlei in
 vancung khua lam ah, &quot;Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai&quot;

[C1]
   Kan hmuhsak lai, Kan hmuhsak lai, Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai, Vawlei
   in vacung khua lam ah Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai.

[V2]
 Sual fawrhnak na zuan deng tikah, Na hawi nih an hlawt ahcun,
 Bia-karnak kha na lung chungah Kan hmuhsak nak na zumh lai.

[C2]
   Kan hmuhsak lai, Kan hmuhsak lai, Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai, Vawlei
   in vacung khua lam ah Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai.

[V3]
 Na ruahchan lung a rawh tikah, A tlau dih ngaingai ahcun, Bawi Jesuh a
 biakam nak kha, Na lung i thle law va zum.

[C3]
   Kan hmuhsak lai, Kan hmuhsak lai, Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai, Vawlei
   in vacung khua lam ah Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai.

[V4]
 Thihnak khua a muih deng tikah, Na thihnak lai caan a nai, Na Bawipa
 au thawng va ngai tuah, &quot;Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai&quot;.

[C4]
   Kan hmuhsak lai, Kan hmuhsak lai, Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai, Vawlei
   in vacung khua lam ah Ka mit in kan hmuhsak lai.</lyrics>
</song>